<br>
I am a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> summoner</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> and I like helping my guild with focus, trod and resist gear. If I compute ALL damages that everyone does just because I was here at begining, it is wonderfull <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
And COH, of course ! We had lots of raids which last more than 5 hours, and where COH was mandatory to have new players coming : think about Euro/US players : we start raid with euro at 8 CET - that's 2 EST - play 5 hours then US members come and go on<br>
<br>
I am a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> caster</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> and from time to time it is a funny thing to see I am in a KS group in a raid with other mages or wizzies. Others time mob resist and I do nothing. I don't really care.<br>
<br>
I am a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> pet master</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> and in Xp group I rock, and in a little raid of 2 or 3 groups, I rock and people like to have me in their group just for the bonus XP coming from kills <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
In big raids, it depends on how well I know the zone. Generally my guild trust me when I summon (they did not when I came), but when in doubt I destroy pet and that's all, not worth the risk.<br>
<br>
When I was under 50, I was the more dangerous member of the groups, my pet could tank rather well, get aggro and let rogue friend turn mob into steak.<br>
We were not often going to raids nor planes. <br>
Now I go to XP groups because I must do it for leveling, but I am bored with that.<br>
I spend 80% my time in raids with my guild and I am just a soldier in an army, a piece in a big mechanism. <br>
let's have a comparison : I've got a friend who is a WARRIOR, level 55. He will never be our Main Tank, but he's happy just fighting with the guild. <br>
I've got another friend who's a level 54 enchanter. He is not our main  mezzer ! he is not with C3 and other level 60 spells. but he stills go to raids because it is fun, and he does his job.<br>
And witout all those guys, raids would just failed. I am one of them.<br>
<br>
May be I am going to be bored with that next year ? well, we will see... <br>
<br>
<br>
I have no alt.  <p><TABLE border=1 bgcolor="#80ff00">
